  "detailed_description": "Confront alien silicon-based lifeform bosses：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920380/extras/50c6552f1d9387cce178f69fbd5e97a3.poster.avif?t=1730789066\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920380/extras/50c6552f1d9387cce178f69fbd5e97a3.webm?t=1730789066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920380/extras/50c6552f1d9387cce178f69fbd5e97a3.mp4?t=1730789066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect monster genes for genetic editing, continuously enhancing them! Make them bigger, bigger, and even bigger, until they become colossal titans!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920380/extras/b249cfb4284a6b5db14a9a6c4789c6a7.poster.avif?t=1730789066\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920380/extras/b249cfb4284a6b5db14a9a6c4789c6a7.webm?t=1730789066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920380/extras/b249cfb4284a6b5db14a9a6c4789c6a7.mp4?t=1730789066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hundreds of recruitable tactical battle units with a standalone tower defense battle mode:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920380/extras/c82c6ae87492fa2a9a929f6fc2b6eb9a.poster.avif?t=1730789066\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920380/extras/c82c6ae87492fa2a9a929f6fc2b6eb9a.webm?t=1730789066\" type=\"video/webm;